initialize

void initialize()
Initialize the child components of this ThingView. Must be called by the client after the ThingView has been constructed and has been added, as a widget, to the widget hierarchy in which it will reside.

getFragmentId

java.lang.String getFragmentId()
The URL fragment identifier assigned to this Thing View. The fragment identifier is a way for the view to save information in the URL about the state of the view.
